description: This file is the entry point for a Qwik-based web application, specifically serving as the bundle entry for 'npm run preview'. It sets up the QwikCity middleware with a render function and a plan, facilitating the preview of the built app in production mode.

methods.name: createQwikCity
methods.description: Creates and configures the QwikCity middleware with the provided render function and plan, facilitating the server-side rendering setup for the app.
